{"article_id":"okjl6d6WMAucfh22","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"At least 28 states are not following US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention guidelines","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"on reporting new Covid-19 cases","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"-- half of which saw the trend of new cases increasing in the last week .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Those states are not reporting probable cases ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"according to the daily case count","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"listed on the CDC 's website .","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"Probable cases include those","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"that show evidence of an infection","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"without the confirmation of a lab test","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"and cases","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"where coronavirus was listed as a cause or contributing cause of death","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"but are not confirmed with a lab test .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"Some of the states with the largest populations","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"-- like California , Florida , New York and Texas --","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"are among those","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"listed as not reporting probable cases ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"despite CDC guidance","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that they should be included in the case count .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"This comes","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"as 26 states see an increased or steady rate of new cases .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Accurate rates of new cases are among the metrics","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that help officials track how the disease is spreading in the US","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and make decisions","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"about how to reopen and loosen restrictions","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"put in place","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to mitigate its impact .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"More than 1.9 million Americans have been infected ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and more than 111,000 have died in just over four months ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"according to data from Johns Hopkins University .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Though coronavirus reporting guidelines are voluntary ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"states","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"not reporting probable cases","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"likely undercount the number of people infected","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and make it difficult for officials to get the true picture of where the nation stands in the midst of a pandemic","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that has rocked almost every aspect of life .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Schools have been especially upended ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"with students across the country not having been on campus in months .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"While many local governments have expressed","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that the path forward for the fall is unclear ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"North Carolina and California have released guidelines","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"for reopening schools .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Though California 's 1,000 school districts will make their own decision","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"about how and when to resume in-classroom learning ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"the state 's Department of Education released a 62-page guidebook Monday","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to help them plan ahead of time .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"The guide gives options for staggered schedules , ongoing distance learning , and models","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that combine both .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"It also directs educators to teach proper handwashing","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and limits the number of students","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"allowed on buses","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to prevent the virus from breaking out in schools .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"`` This guidance is only as good","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"as what 's implemented , ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"State Superintendent Tony Thurmond said in a news conference .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"`` We expect","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"it will be adjusted","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"as we go . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"North Carolina Gov . Roy Cooper also released health guidance","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"for reopening schools Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"telling reporters","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that this school year will be unlike any other .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"`` Students and staff will be screened for illness","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"before they enter the school .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Children will be asked to stay distant from classmates .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"They wo n't be sharing pencils or textbooks ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and there will be a lot of cleaning , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Openings will depend on health metrics ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"But state Secretary of Health and Human Services Dr. Mandy Cohen is concerned","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the state 's positive tests are among the highest in the nation ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"she said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"`` These trends moving in the wrong direction is a signal","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"we need to take very seriously , ''","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Cohen said during a news conference .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"While North Carolina is seeing cases rise ,","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"California","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"-- with trends holding steady --","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"is beginning to reopen some recreational sites .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Yosemite National Park ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"which has been off-limits to visitors since March 20 ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"will reopen to the public Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"It will aim to admit only half of its average visitor rate ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"beginning by allowing 1,700 vehicle passes each day ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"according a statement from park spokesman Jamie Richards .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` There is no place like Yosemite ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and we ca n't wait to welcome visitors back , ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"said Acting Superintendent Cicely Muldoon .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"`` It 's going to be a different kind of summer ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"and we will continue to work hand in hand with our gateway communities","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"to protect community health","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and restore access to Yosemite National Park . ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"As early as Friday , indoor California movie theaters may reopen ,","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"according to guidance","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"the California Department of Public Health released on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Theaters are required to limit attendees to 25 % of capacity or a maximum of 100 attendees , whichever is lower .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Theaters will also need to reconfigure seats","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"to ensure physical distancing between moviegoers ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"who must wear face coverings","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"when not eating or drinking","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"to mitigate virus spread ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"the guidance says .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"As many of the hardest hit states begin to recover from the pandemic ,","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"cases have risen elsewhere .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Vermont ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"where new cases are increasing ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"had an outbreak","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"reported Friday","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"with at least 62 people infected near Winooski ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Vermont Health Commissioner Dr. Mark Levine said .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Dozens of children were among those infected ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"and more than 1,000 people in the state went","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"to get tested","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"following the outbreak ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Levine said .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Vermont State Epidemiologist Patsy Kelso said","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"the outbreak was spread by friends and relatives ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"and through contact tracing","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"it appears to be well-contained .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"In Utah , state Rep. Suzanne Harrison called a recent spike of cases `` very concerning","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"( and ) approaching exponential . ''","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"The positive test rate doubled from one day to the next to 18.5 % ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"she tweeted over the weekend .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"`` When you 're away from home ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"please avoid close contact with others ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"and wear a mask","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"when other social distancing measures are n't feasible , ''","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the Utah Department of Health tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"In the last week , Texas and Arizona have seen spikes in cases ,","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"with both reporting more than 1,000 new cases in one day .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Several universities have also reported new cases within their athletic programs","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"-- including Arkansas State University , Auburn University and Oklahoma State University .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":0,"right":264,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":264,"left":207,"right":263,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":169,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":161,"right":168,"relatio